This is the package "elsarticle-ecrc" for generating CRC journal articles using the Elsevier LaTeX document class elsarticle.

This version 1.2 dated 09 May 2011
************************************************************

The following files are included:
* The elsarticle document class, elsarticle.cls
* The documentation, elsdoc.pdf
* A bibliographic style file for the numbered reference style, elsarticle-num.bst
* The package file for Elsevier CRC, ecrc.sty
* Sample journal logo files elsevier-logo-3p, SDlogo-3p (in PDF and PS format)
* A template manuscript file, ecrc-template.tex

All the above are also available at http://www.elsevier.com/latex

(NB other bibliographic styles are available on the main elsarticle page, but Elsevier CRC generally uses a numbered reference style)


To use:
1. Unpack all the files into the same folder
2. Edit the manuscript file ecrc-template.tex according to the instructions in that file, and save with a new name
3. Compile with PDFLaTeX (and BibTeX if desired)


**************************************************************
*                                                            *
* Important note on usage                                    *
* -----------------------                              	     *
* Files using ecrc should normally be compiled with PDFLaTeX *
* Using standard LaTeX should work, but may produce clashes  *
*                                                            *
**************************************************************

